title: Over Zealous (w/ Ali Siddiq, Chris Cotton & Roy Wood Jr.)
description: Ali Siddiq & Chris Cotton join the show, and it turns out he's wearing a wire. Jay and Christine share a Facetime mishap. Roy Wood Jr. discusses morning radio and being an extra on movie sets.
